    "It is also possible to define multiple PanDA queues for a single batch queue, allowing them to share worker nodes underneath.",
    "A PanDA queue is associated with one or more storage resources for automatic data motion, which is described in Sect.",
    "\"Automatic Data Distribution and Aggregation\".",
    "Virtual OrganizationA virtual organization (VO) refers to a dynamic set of individuals defined around a set of resource-sharing rules and conditions.",
